CODING STYLE IN SISAL

1996-04-20: Building an array via catenate style is really really slow.
            This method:

%Fragment sl 111          Replicate vector-vector
function $FNAME(x1: array[$XTYPE];
                y1: array[$YTYPE] 
                returns array[$ZTYPE])  
 array_setl(for i in SISALIO,
    SISALIO+ConformSameLength(array_size(x1),array_size(y1))-1
  returns value of catenate
  array_fill(SISALIO,SISALIO+(ConformNonNegativeInt($XTtoI(x1[i])))-1,y1[i])
 end for,SISALIO)
end function

is about 25x slower (compiota 5e6) than:

%Fragment sl 111 b c c Replicate vector-vector
function $FNAME(x1: array[$XTYPE];
                y1: array[$YTYPE] 
                returns array[$ZTYPE])  
 array_setl(for x0 in x1 at i
            returns array of y1[i] when x0
            end for,SISALIO)
end function


